					"value": "Load up CTY_Main_A\r\nuse the debugbook>Set quest flags & options > Act3(LOW/END) > LOW - Steel Watch Foundry > choose any option\r\nTeleport to -267; 6; -148 and go throught he dialog that starts\r\nUse Killcombat to end the fight.\r\nStart the dialog by clicking on S_LOW_GondianWorker08_Leader_3607ec31-f939-41aa-a7d2-e32f8c46979d"
